  <resortCombinations><![CDATA[<p>To experience more of Liguria, we’d recommend pairing a stay on Alassio with a few days on one of the eastern towns like <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/liguria/sestri-levante">Sestri Levante</a> or <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/liguria/portovenere">Portovenere</a> where you’ll be on the doorstep of the Cinque Terre. You can also hire a car and drive to one of Italy most picturesque lakes – <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-como">Lake Como</a>, which is about three and half hours away.</p>]]></resortCombinations>
